TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed HtmlTextWriterTag extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: Specifies the HTML tags that can be passed to an or object output stream.

remarks.format:
## Remarks This enumeration allows the output stream to write HTML mark up, along with HTML server controls, in response to a Web request.
## Examples The following example demonstrates the use of the HtmlTextWriterTag enumeration. The Img field is used during rendering of an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> named `writer`.
[!code-vb[System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter#3](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/t-system.web.ui.htmltext_2_1.vb)] [!code-cs[System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter#3](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/t-system.web.ui.htmltext_2_1.cs)] [!code-cpp[System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter#3](~/add/codesnippet/cpp/t-system.web.ui.htmltext_2_1.cpp)]
